room_title: Escape room "Missing Starlet" by Hysterium Escapes in Fort Wayne
room_description:
Step back in time to 1952. You have entered the dressing room of a famous Hollywood starlet, but she is nowhere to be found! Upon investigation, you discover that she may have been murdered!
Is she the girlfriend of the elusive Secret Agent 22? Did Agent 22 flee because he was a suspect in murder? Perhaps the Starlet is not dead at all? Can you and your date crack the case and escape the room before the possible killer returns?
